com.opcoach.training.rental
Interface Customer

All Known Implementing Classes:
CustomerImpl
public interface Customer

A representation of the model object 'Customer'.

The following features are supported:

  • First Name
  • Last Name
  • Address
  • Licenses
  • Parent Agency
